items.title: Shooting reported at Catholic school in Minneapolis, shooter 'contained'
items.description: A shooting has been reported at Annunciation Catholic School in Minneapolis, according to Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz.

items.title: Judge blocks administration from deporting Abrego Garcia until at least October
items.description: A federal judge has temporarily blocked the Trump administration from deporting Kilmar Abrego Garcia until at least early October.

items.description: 24/7 coverage of breaking news and live events

items.title: Coco Gauff secures 1st round win at US Open after nearly 3-hour match
items.description: Coco Gauff advanced past the U.S. Open first round after a nearly three-hour match at Arthur Ashe Stadium.

items.title: WATCH:  Cracker Barrel says new logo is ‘going away’ after rebranding backlash
items.description: Cracker Barrel announced in a statement it is returning to its old logo amid outcry from fans and even President Donald Trump.
